- Luis…

562
00:36:35,666 --> 00:36:36,666
Lide!

563
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:40,541
The keys. Now.

564
00:36:40,625 --> 00:36:42,083
No! Stop!

565
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:46,500
- Just let her check.
- Lide!

566
