- Good, Mara!

603
00:39:57,833 --> 00:40:00,375
Because I didn't touch her.

604
00:40:01,125 --> 00:40:02,583
- Where is she?
- I don't know.

605
00:40:03,375 --> 00:40:04,500
I don't know, Mara.

606
