- I was--
- Shut up.

743
00:49:00,375 --> 00:49:02,916
And about the bracelet, Mara…

744
00:49:03,416 --> 00:49:05,083
- It was on the ground.
- Mara!

745
00:49:08,583 --> 00:49:09,583
Mara.

746
