Don't let him go.

747
00:49:12,916 --> 00:49:14,291
Check the rope.

748
00:49:14,375 --> 00:49:15,458
You're not listening.

749
00:49:15,541 --> 00:49:17,125
- Shut up.
- You're not listening.

750
