You didn't let me explain.

752
00:49:55,500 --> 00:49:56,833
Where's my daughter?

753
00:49:59,708 --> 00:50:01,208
I don't know.

754
00:50:03,625 --> 00:50:05,833
She can't just disappear.

755
00:50:06,750 --> 00:50:08,625
Listen, I…

756
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:13,791
